 happening in your life, that there is hardship,

781
00:38:54,200 --> 00:38:56,400
 you want to follow God but it was so hard

782
00:38:57,840 --> 00:39:02,360
 that you were let down, sometimes you were even criticized,

783
00:39:02,360 --> 00:39:04,360
 sometimes or all the time you feel,

784
00:39:04,360 --> 00:39:06,440
 well, you're not good enough,

785
00:39:06,440 --> 00:39:08,960
 or all that whatever you're going through.

786
00:39:08,960 --> 00:39:14,160
 I don't want to be harsh but I do want to say,

787
00:39:14,160 --> 00:39:18,400
 congratulations, God is at work in your life.

788
00:39:18,400 --> 00:39:22,680
 If he sees us as those unfruitful branch,

789
00:39:22,680 --> 00:39:25,000
 he will simply just cut us off.

790
00:39:26,080 --> 00:39:27,640
 But if God is still at work in you,

791
00:39:27,640 --> 00:39:30,560
 that means there must be an area in your life

792
00:39:30,560 --> 00:39:33,120
 that you have already started to bear fruit.

793
00:39:33,120 --> 00:39:37,040
 So don't get discouraged.

794
00:39:37,040 --> 00:39:40,920
 I know how hard sometimes it could be

795
00:39:40,920 --> 00:39:44,240
 to fail again and again in life,

796
00:39:44,240 --> 00:39:46,120
 to get rejected again and again in life,

797
00:39:46,120 --> 00:39:48,520
 to feel you're not good enough, you don't measure up.

798
00:39:48,520 --> 00:39:50,000
 I know how it feels.

799
00:39:50,000 --> 00:39:53,080
 But God is not done yet.

800
00:39:53,960 --> 00:39:57,640
 He is the gardener, he is the good and faithful one.

801
00:39:57,640 --> 00:40:00,240
 He says, if I'm going to start a work inside of you,

802
00:40:00,240 --> 00:40:02,160
 I'm going to finish it myself.

803
00:40:02,160 --> 00:40:06,320
 And his presence is in this room today.

804
00:40:06,320 --> 00:40:12,200
 The gardener, God the Father, is looking down.

805
00:40:12,200 --> 00:40:16,160
 He saw the branches here in this room.

806
00:40:16,160 --> 00:40:21,800
 And he said, you will always be my plan A for this world.

807
00:40:22,920 --> 00:40:26,760
 I will always bless this world

808
00:40:26,760 --> 00:40:29,640
 through the branches of the true vine, Jesus.

809
00:40:29,640 --> 00:40:34,960
 So why don't we just come before him?

810
00:40:34,960 --> 00:40:36,760
 Why don't we just come back to the source,

811
00:40:36,760 --> 00:40:39,440
 come back to the vine, the true vine,

812
00:40:39,440 --> 00:40:41,960
 say, God, I surrender.

813
00:40:41,960 --> 00:40:45,280
 I want to remain in you.

814
00:40:45,280 --> 00:40:46,960
 I want to remain in your love.

815
00:40:46,960 --> 00:40:51,800
 This is where I feel hard to follow your word.

816
00:40:51,800 --> 00:40:54,520
 This is where I couldn't align my lifestyle

817
00:40:54,520 --> 00:40:55,720
 with your word yet.

818
00:40:55,720 --> 00:40:57,320
 Please come and prune me.

819
00:40:57,320 --> 00:41:02,400
 You know, the Bible says,

820
00:41:02,400 --> 00:41:04,360
 Jesus, for the joy that is set before him,

821
00:41:04,360 --> 00:41:07,400
 he endure the suffering.

822
00:41:07,400 --> 00:41:10,480
 Pruning feels like that, it's like a suffering.

823
00:41:10,480 --> 00:41:13,120
 You will not enjoy pruning.

824
00:41:13,120 --> 00:41:15,480
 Pruning is something that you have to endure,

825
00:41:15,480 --> 00:41:19,800
 but the real joy, it's what's beyond it.

826
00:41:21,520 --> 00:41:26,520
 I'm not asking you to enjoy being pruned.

827
00:41:26,520 --> 00:41:28,760
 I'm asking you to endure being pruned

828
00:41:28,760 --> 00:41:31,440
 so that you can finally, one day,

829
00:41:31,440 --> 00:41:34,240
 enjoy the fruitfulness in your life.

830
00:41:34,240 --> 00:41:37,520
 Areas in your life you will reflect the glory of the Father

831
00:41:37,520 --> 00:41:39,840
 and the love of Jesus.

832
00:41:39,840 --> 00:41:43,760
 It's possible because he is capable.

833
00:41:43,760 --> 00:41:48,560
 It's Christmas, why don't we come back to him?

834
00:41:48,560 --> 00:41:52,120
 Why don't we stand, stand together?

835
00:41:52,120 --> 00:42:02,160
 If you would like to,

836
00:42:02,160 --> 00:42:06,600
 you may open up your hands,

837
00:42:06,600 --> 00:42:09,160
 it's just a gesture, a posture,

838
00:42:09,160 --> 00:42:11,480
 telling God, God, I'm here, I surrender.

839
00:42:11,480 --> 00:42:16,240
 Say to him, God, I'm struggling in this area.

840
00:42:17,480 --> 00:42:20,520
 I know my life does not align with the word

841
00:42:20,520 --> 00:42:22,480
 that you have put in me yet.

842
00:42:22,480 --> 00:42:25,280
 Help me, come and prune me, God.

843
00:42:25,280 --> 00:42:31,120
 Until my life reflects the life of Jesus,

844
00:42:31,120 --> 00:42:34,800
 until his life is overflowing in me

845
00:42:34,800 --> 00:42:39,800
 and expressed itself as the fruits in my life,

846
00:42:39,800 --> 00:42:42,960
 the joy, the peace,

847
00:42:44,720 --> 00:42:47,720
 the love that I show the people around me,

848
00:42:47,720 --> 00:42:49,880
 until I look like Jesus,

849
00:42:49,880 --> 00:42:52,720
 until this city of Hong Kong, this area of Yuen Long

850
00:42:52,720 --> 00:42:54,880
 is filled with branches walking around

851
00:42:54,880 --> 00:42:57,600
 and they're all displaying the DNA of the vine,

852
00:42:57,600 --> 00:42:59,920
 they're all displaying the character of Jesus,

853
00:42:59,920 --> 00:43:02,440
 they're all displaying the power of the Holy Spirit.

854
00:43:02,440 --> 00:43:04,760
 Father, before that, we pray you will come

855
00:43:04,760 --> 00:43:08,840
 and continue to prune the branches in this church.

856
00:43:08,840 --> 00:43:14,360
 Come and prune me, Lord.

857
00:43:14,360 --> 00:43:16,940
 (gentle music)

